{"type": "article", "id": 18081, "title": "卫生纸包装", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-26T07:20:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 79, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702134810m0O8SjFNsJ7qMW3A.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t水果和卫生纸几乎是没有共同点的物品，但日本设计师 Kazuaki Kawahara 还是将它们联系在一起。卷筒卫生纸外包了一层“果皮”，上下露出里面的“瓤”，立刻让普通的卷纸变得“秀色可餐”。他选择了奇异果、西瓜、草莓和橘子 4 种水果，在圆筒的上下折叠成褶皱，与光滑的皮对比，让“果实”显得很丰富。4 个组成一套，售价 1500 日元，<a href=\"http://latona-m.onlinestores.jp/category/select/cid/312/pid/8764\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134808EipqXg4OTcU3vkej.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6675\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134808Aeh9PvSMNcQoYKXb.jpg\" width=\"650\" height=\"433\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66615385\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134809mP3Uc9YaVpTSZxhu.jpg\" width=\"650\" height=\"433\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66615385\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134809d3XUwWIAVvYp7tcJ.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"604\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.755\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n"}